dct_title_s: Map of route from the Tati settlement to Delagoa Bay to illustrate the paper by Captn. F. Elton
dct_description_sm: Captain Elton's route shown in red. Dates and locations of of camps are shown. Relief shown by hachures. Includes information on vegetation, wildlife, and soil quality. Locations of kraals along route are shown. From: Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 42 (1872), pp. 1-49; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v.42 1872.
dct_publisher_sm: London : published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society, by J. Murray, Albemarle Street, 1872.
